Intro.text: Our buddy Grabsy is a spider monkey who lives in the South American Rainforest.
Chris and I are traveling through the Rainforest to gather as much fruit as we can for the party!
We are also on the lookout for other monkeys from Grabsy's troop to invite them to the party!
There are a few Power Creature Discs along the path. Keep an eye out for them!
They'll be help you get around the Rainforest and get out of jams.
Walk left and right by pressing the left and right arrow keys on the keyboard.

Final.text: Excellent! We've gathered Grabsy's troop for the birthday party!
Look at all this fruit! Thank you for making Grabsy's birthday party a big success!
